					<p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-2"><strong>School district:</strong> Leander ISD</p>
					<p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Cedar Park's east side is a 20-minute drive to Dell; the west side adds another 10 minutes but rewards with larger lots and top-ranked Leander ISD schools. See the <a href="/neighborhoods/cedar-park" class="text-accent no-underline hover:underline">Cedar Park guide</a>.</p>
