					<p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-2"><strong>Price range:</strong> $375K–$560K</p>
					<p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-2"><strong>School district:</strong> Pflugerville ISD</p>
					<p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Pflugerville offers the best value for Dell employees willing to commute 20 minutes. The TX-45 connection to Round Rock avoids I-35. New construction is the primary option. See the <a href="/neighborhoods/pflugerville" class="text-accent no-underline hover:underline">Pflugerville guide</a>.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl p-6">
					<h3 class="font-display font-bold text-primary mb-3">Hutto</h3>
