					<p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-2"><strong>School district:</strong> Hutto ISD</p>
					<p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Hutto is the price-conscious option — best dollars-per-square-foot in the Dell commute corridor. A good fit for first-time buyers or those prioritizing space over commute time.</p>
