					<p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Zilker and Barton Hills are some of the most desirable neighborhoods in Austin — Barton Springs Pool, Zilker Park, the hike-and-bike trail, and proximity to downtown. Premium prices but some of the best resale stability in the city.</p>
